    "Figure 5: nonrecursive relationship between y i and y j Second, for system dynamics models, we will generally require B 3 and B 4 to be of lower triangular matrices with a zero diagonals since one of the basic principles of system dynamics is that every feedback loop must have at least one stock variable.",
